    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/f8bfc7867ebe4b4d8ed7932107837b6b.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造和扩展你可爱的兔子小镇</h2>创建一个繁荣的社区，每个居民都是可爱的小兔子。随着更多兔子的加入，看着你的小镇不断成长。欣赏精美的像素艺术风格，让你的兔子小镇栩栩如生。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/7ebdd88e30ecdbad3fd9565f718514b4.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/7ebdd88e30ecdbad3fd9565f718514b4.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/7ebdd88e30ecdbad3fd9565f718514b4.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >防御或征服</h2>训练一支毛茸茸的军队来保护你的小镇或突袭帝国据点。观看激动人心的战斗，你的兔子战士为你的事业而战。更喜欢和平体验？尽情享受游戏的轻松和平模式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/bafc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/bafc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/bafc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握建筑组合</h2>发现每个建筑独特的相邻加成。尝试不同的组合以最大化效率。适应随机生成的地图，获得无尽的可重玩性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁新的游戏方式</h2>在建筑选择、升级、贸易和研究方面做出有意义的选择。随着进度的推进和成功，发现新的策略。解锁令人兴奋的内容，包括新的城镇类型、独特的市政厅、额外特权和具有挑战性的难度级别。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
